com.esri.mo2.map.img
Interface ServerImage

All Superinterfaces:
Data, Image, MapData, Spatial
All Known Implementing Classes:
BaseServerImage
public interface ServerImage
extends Image

A simple geo-referenced image. The image is assumed to be alligned with the coordinate system, that is, no rotation or shear is involved in the transform.

load

public void load(URL u,
                 ActionListener listener)
          throws Exception
Starts loading the Image using the given URL; notifies the ActionListener when loading begins and on completion. ActionEvents sent to the listener will have ID property set to one of the identifiers BEGUN, COMPLETE, or ERROR.

Parameters:
u - the URL location of the Image
listener - notified when retrieval is complete
Exception
See Also:
BEGUN, COMPLETE, ERROR
